    Akron sent a pair of energon bolts from both hands this time, and rolled 
out of the way. She was tense, but this was the kind of excitement she like. 
As she took out her energon riffle, she watched the bots scatter.
    
    Nighteyes took a hit in her shoulder plate, which sent her flying into 
the tree behinde her. With a pillar of smoke rising from her shoulder, she 
took out her pistol and shot Drillbit.
